    <item>
      <title>法国总统阿尔芒谈预算、勒庞和赤字目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/france-s-armand-on-budget-le-pen-and-deficit-targets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长安托万·阿尔芒 (Antoine Armand) 与彭博电视台的卡罗琳·科南 (Caroline Connan) 进行了交谈，此时法国正面临预算政治危机，而玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 领导的国民联盟的让步期限也迫在眉睫。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/france-s-armand-on-budget-le-pen-and-deficit-targets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔芒：法国不能动摇预算赤字目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/armand-france-can-t-waver-on-budget-deficit-targets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长安托万·阿尔芒 (Antoine Armand) 告诉彭博电视台的卡罗琳·科南 (Caroline Connan)，动摇削减预算赤字的承诺“不是一种选择”。他在法国极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 就新预算法设定的最后期限之前发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/armand-france-can-t-waver-on-budget-deficit-targets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔芒称法国政府不会受到勒索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/armand-says-the-french-government-won-t-be-blackmailed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长安托万·阿尔芒 (Antoine Armand) 告诉彭博电视台的卡罗琳·科南 (Caroline Connan)，法国政府不会接受玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 就新预算法设定的人为期限。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-01/armand-says-the-french-government-won-t-be-blackmailed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:03:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国奢侈品需求减弱，宝格丽首席执行官看好印度市场增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/bulgari-ceo-eyes-india-for-growth-as-china-luxury-demand-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 旗下的珠宝商宝格丽 (Bulgari) 希望通过印度来缓解中国经济放缓带来的奢侈品需求下滑的影响。]]></description>
